metadata.description:
1 of 2,222 Feature³ Founder’s Passes and your ticket to receiving the Feature³ Founder’s Edition Device - the world’s first blockchain-enabled streaming device.

In addition to receiving this special edition device, holders of the Feature³ Founder’s Pass enjoy a variety of unique utility benefits. Own the original edition of the device that’s changing everything, and bring the metaverse into your living room.

Discover more about Feature³ at feature.io

Join the conversation at discord.com/invite/feature
